<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; text-align: center;">
    <h1 style="color: #007bff; margin: 0;">Booking Received!</h1>
  </div>
  
  <div style="padding: 20px;">
    <p>Dear {{customerName}},</p>
    
    <p>Thank you for booking with Car Rental. We have received your booking and it is currently <strong>pending approval</strong> by our team. Here are your booking details:</p>
    
    <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #333;">Booking Details</h3>
      <p><strong>Booking ID:</strong> {{bookingDetails.id}}</p>
      <p><strong>Start Date:</strong> {{bookingDetails.startDate}}</p>
      <p><strong>End Date:</strong> {{bookingDetails.endDate}}</p>
      <p><strong>Total Price:</strong> ${{bookingDetails.totalPrice}}</p>
      <p><strong>Status:</strong> <span style="color: #ffc107; font-weight: bold;">{{bookingDetails.status}}</span></p>
    </div>
    
    <p>We will review your booking and send you a confirmation email once it has been approved by our team.</p>
    <p>If you have any questions or need to make changes, please contact our customer service team.</p>
    
    <div style="margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6;">
      <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px;">
        Best regards,<br>
        Car Rental Team<br>
        <strong>Submission Date:</strong> {{submissionDate}}
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div> 